data.description: 2.25% Assumable Rate!* Discover unparalleled luxury in this extraordinary Bartram Springs residence. This one-of-a-kind home stands alone in its uniqueness, boasting brand new 8' doors and windows that usher in natural light, creating an ambiance of elegance and warmth. A picturesque koi pond and a swim spa, the same kind favored by Olympian Michael Phelps, grace the preserve lot, offering a serene outdoor oasis. Indoors, artistic inspiration comes to life in the Jackson Pollock-inspired living room, while a secret soundproofed room provides a private retreat. Luxury vinyl plank flooring seamlessly flows throughout, complementing the modern design. The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring custom epoxy countertops, double stacked cabinets with lighting, and upgraded stainless steel..... appliances, including a convenient pot filler. Entertain effortlessly with the Bose surround system and the linear fireplace with built-in shelving. Enjoy the convenience of a cedar-lined master shower with a rainfall shower head and multi-jet system, adding a spa-like touch to your daily routine. The home also offers a double French door office, a screened lanai, and a custom 16' wine storage and buffet in the dining room. Storage is abundant with custom closets and a 3-car garage featuring overhead storage solutions. A unique fish tank embedded into the wall completes this unparalleled living experience, making this property a true gem in Bartram Springs.
